### About Me
I am currently an undergrad at IISc Bangalore. I am interested in modeling in biological science, especially neuroscience. Currently I am working on such a project with [Dr. Upi Bhalla](https://www.ncbs.res.in/bhalla) at NCBS.

You can find my github page at Pritish Patil (@iampritishpatil).
